tn.misc

Class LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tn.misc.LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GameMethod.Game.CostProperty, LinkNormalizedProperty, LinkProperty, LinkPropertyFunction, LinkPropertyStatistics.RankProperty, ScaledLinkProperty, TrafficNetwork.FlowCostFunction, TTGrader.DelayedResult

    public abstract class LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Description:

    This class is the base class for creating a link property. As the name implies, it creates a "read-only" property. Therefore, it has only getter methods to get desired property-associated values. All property values must be convertable to Double. Instantiating this abstract class and implementing its methods enables the creation of a read-only link property of a specified type "T".
